Blackstone Group LP (BX)  is in talks to
buy the London headquarters of  Aon Corp. (AON)  in a 330 million-pound
($524 million) deal, the Sunday Times reported, without saying
how it obtained the information.  The asset is owned by Rockpoint Group LLC and Abu Dhabi
Investment Authority, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
